      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A. Bingo Candies\ntime limit per test1 second\nmemory limit per test256 megabytes",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A. Bingo Candies\ntime limit per test1 second\nmemory limit per test256 megabytes",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bmGYmmKrSw0Xl0BNc6ZGn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3855.1327189322014,
      "y": 115.52610949030799,
      "width": 1073.791259765625,
      "height": 120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b17",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1310055069,
      "version": 242,
      "versionNonce": 345056568,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773743774797,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Alice has a magic board. The board is described as a n×n grid; each tile has a colored candy in it. The color of the candy in the i-th row,\n j-th column is ai,j.\n\nBob wants to know if he can rearrange the board in some way so that no row or column consists of n candies of the same color.\n\nYour task is to determine whether such a rearrangement exists.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Alice has a magic board. The board is described as a n×n grid; each tile has a colored candy in it. The color of the candy in the i-th row,\n j-th column is ai,j.\n\nBob wants to know if he can rearrange the board in some way so that no row or column consists of n candies of the same color.\n\nYour task is to determine whether such a rearrangement exists.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9tBpYM9Vg-tWsD4CtC4_c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3856.6192386593702,
      "y": 252.56678107691005,
      "width": 39.15196228027344,
      "height": 18.4,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b19",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 985229309,
      "version": 154,
      "versionNonce": 342420040,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773743774797,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Input",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Input",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "1CdKSrIEXOi0InwwopRvz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3852.8416651583993,
      "y": 281.5460720033002,
      "width": 1078.041748046875,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1A",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1753471347,
      "version": 145,
      "versionNonce": 1923595832,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773743774797,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Each test contains multiple test cases. The first line contains the number of test cases t(1≤t≤500). The description of the test cases \nfollows.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains an integer n(1≤n≤100), denoting the size of the board.\n\nThe following n lines contain n integers each; the j-th integer on the i-th line is ai,j(1≤ai,j≤n2), denoting the color of candies on the \nboard.\n\nIt is guaranteed that the sum of n over all test cases does not exceed 500.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Each test contains multiple test cases. The first line contains the number of test cases t(1≤t≤500). The description of the test cases \nfollows.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains an integer n(1≤n≤100), denoting the size of the board.\n\nThe following n lines contain n integers each; the j-th integer on the i-th line is ai,j(1≤ai,j≤n2), denoting the color of candies on the \nboard.\n\nIt is guaranteed that the sum of n over all test cases does not exceed 500.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Gd6z_xjgrGRSa0auA7603",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3852.4076385247313,
      "y": 479.85178615131224,
      "width": 49.19993591308594,
      "height": 18.4,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
